owl:Ontology.terms:creator: MiHyun Jang
Neda Jahanshad
Ryan Espiritu
owl:Ontology.terms:title: The Cohort Ontology
owl:Ontology.rdfs:comment: A cohort ontology that describes cohorts and their properties.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A homepage for some thing.

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 didNotHaveFirstEpisodeOf Psychosis --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who had a first episode of psychosis
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which diseases the cohort group members did NOT have a first episode of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: did not have first episode of

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 doesNotHaveCondition euthymia
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which disease conditions are excluded in a given cohort group
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: does not have condition

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveDisorder Cancer --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who have cancer
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which disorders are excluded in a given cohort group
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: does not have disorder

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveFamilyHistoryOf Schizophrenia --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who have a family history of schizophrenia
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which diseases the cohort group members do NOT have a family history of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: does not family history of

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveFirstDegreeRelativeWithDisorder BipolarDisorder --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who have a first degree relative with bipolar disorder
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which diseases the first degree relatives of cohort group members do NOT have
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: does not first degree relative with disorder

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveHistoryOf NeurologicalDisease --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who have neurological disease
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the diseases that the cohort group members do NOT have a history of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: does not have personal history of

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotUseTreatment Antidepressants --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who use antidepressants
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which medications or therapies that the cohort group members are NOT using
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: does not use treatment

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: bipolarDisorder fulfillsDiagnosticCriteria diagnosticAndStatisticalManualOfMentalDisorders --> The diagnosis of bipolar disorder fulfills the criteria of the DSM
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the criteria used to diagnose the disorder
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: fulfills diagnostic criteria

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasBrainScanDataType MRI
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the brain scan data types that were collected for a cohort or project
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has brain scan data type

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasCondition euthymia
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which diease conditions are included in a given cohort group
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has condition

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: BipolarCohort hasContact JohnSmith
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Property that points to the person that is a contact for the project or cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has contact

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: BipolarCohort hasControlGroup BipolarControlGroup
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the control group of a cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has control group

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasDataType dataType1
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the data types that a cohort or project collected
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has data type

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Property that links a project cohort with the data being described.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has dataset

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasDiagnosisInstrument miniInternationalNeuropychiatricInterview --> The members of Cohort1 are diagnosed with Mini International Neuropychiatric Interview
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes what instrument is used to diagnose the members of the cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has diagnosis instrument

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: BipolarCohort hasPatientGroup BipolarPatientGroup
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the patient group of a cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has diagnostic group

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasDisorder Cancer --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who have cancer
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes what disease(s) the members of the cohort group have
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has disorder

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasDisorderDetails SZ20938
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the details of a particular disorder that a cohort group has
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has disorder details

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasFamilyHistoryOf CardiovascularDisease --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who have a family history of cardiovascular diseases
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes what diseases the members of the cohort group have a family history of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has family history of

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasFirstDegreeRelativeWithDisorder Psychosis --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who have a first degree relative with psychosis
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes what diseases the first degree relatives of the members of the cohort group have
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has first degree relative with disorder

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasFirstEpisodeOf Psychosis --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who had a first episode of psychosis
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes what disease the members of the cohort group had a first episode of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has first episode of

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasGeneticDataType epigenetic
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the genetic data types that were collected for a cohort or project
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has genetic data type

owl:ObjectProperty.vaem:rationale: Property added to facilitate interaction with domain and ranges in the wiki. It's equivalent to foaf:homePage
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Property that describes the home page of a cohort or person
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has home page

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasImageAcquisitionProtocol AcquisitionProtocol1
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the acquisition protocol that was used to scan the data of a cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has image acquisition protocol

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasInformationMethod selfReport --> The information of the members of Cohort1 was obtained through self report
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the method for obtaining the medical information of a cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has information method

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: BipolarCohort hasInvestigator JohnSmith
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describe the investigators of a cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has investigator

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasMainPrincipalInvestigatorof JohnSmith
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which cohorts somone is a main PI of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has main principal investigator

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortDisorderGroup hasMedicalRatingDetails YMRS3010
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the min and max values of the medical rating criteria
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has medical rating details

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1TreatmentInfo usesTreatment Benzodiazepine inThePastMonths 6 --> Cohort1 only includes people who used benzodiazepine in the past6 months
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether or not the members of the cohort had an issue (condition, disorder, or treatment-related) within the past few months
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has members with recent issue

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasHistoryOf NeurologicalDisease --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who have history of neurological disorders
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the disease that the members of the cohort group have a history of
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has personal history of

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: BipolarCohort hasPopulationGroup USCPopulationGroup
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the population group of a population-based cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has population group

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasPrincipalInvestigator John --> the principal investigator of Cohort1 is John
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the principal investigator of the cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has principal investigator

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: BipolarCohort hasProjectCohort BipolarBarcelonaCohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the subcohorts, specific to a given project, that are part of that cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has project cohort

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Property used to link a cohort with the summary statistics that may have been produced after applying a given protocol
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has statistics

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup hasTreatmentDetails antidepressants42
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the details of the treatment that a cohort group is using
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has treatment details

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 analyzedWithGenotypePlatform IllumniaOnmiExpress --> Illumina OnmiExpress was used to analyze cohort1
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes what genotype platform was used to analyze the members of the cohort
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: uses genotype platform

owl:ObjectProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 usesTreatment Antidepressants --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who currently use antidepressants
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes which medications or therapies that the members of the cohort group are using
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: uses treatment

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveComorbidity true --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who are comorbid
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of a cohort group do not have a comorbidity
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: does not have comorbidity

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveContraindicationToMRI yes --> CohortGroup1 excludes people who do have contraindication to MRI
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if individuals who have contraindication to MRI are excluded
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: does not have contraindiction to MRI

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether a cohort excludes people with an intellectual disability
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: does not have intellectual disability

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHaveNeurologicalComorbidity true --> CohortGroup1 does not include people who have two or more neurological disorders
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of a cohort group do not have a neurological comorbidity
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: does not have neurological comorbidity

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 doesNotHavePsychiatricComorbidity true --> CohortGroup1 does not include people who have two or more psychiatric disorders
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of a cohort group do not have a psychiatric comorbidity
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: does not have psychiatric comorbidity

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if left handed people were excluded from the study
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: excludes left hands

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if right handed people were excluded from the study
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: excludes right hands

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the additional demographics defining a given cohort group (Height; Weight; Ethnicity; IQ; ParentalSES; IndividualSES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has additional demographic

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the age groupings of individuals within a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has age group

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the standard deviation of the age of a cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has age standard deviation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the types of brain structural/functional data collected by a cohort group (T1w; dMRI; T2w; SWI; rsfMRI; tbfMRI; ASL; EEG; MEG; Histology; CT; Head Circumference; Cognitive/Behavior assessments)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has brain structural data

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: SZCohort hasBriefDescription "finds correlations between schizophrenia and other conditions"
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Provides a brief description of the working group or project or cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has brief description

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the current status of a cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has cohort status

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes where the data of the cohort was collected
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has collection site

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasComorbidity true --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who are comorbid
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of a cohort group have a comorbidity
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has comorbidity

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the end year of the data collection period of the cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has data collection period end

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the start year of the data collection period of the cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has data collection period start

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment:
Describing the diagnosis disorder of a cohort group
(MDD; Bipolar Disorder; Schizophrenia; OCD; ADHD; HIV; Autism; Addiction / SUD; Epilepsy; Anorexia / Eating Disorders; Parkinson; PTSD; Irritability; Stroke Recovery; Cerebellar Ataxia; Generalized anxiety; Panic disorder; Social anxiety; Early Onset Psychosis; Tourette's Syndrome; Brain Injury; Cancer & Chemotherapy; Sleep; Suicidal Thoughts and Behaviors; Lysosome Storage Diseases; 22q DS; CNVs)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has diagnosis disorder

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the ethnic group that the participants of the cohort are in
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has ethnic group

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the relations between the individuals of a cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has familial relations

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the funding source of the cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has funding source

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the handedness criteria for individuals in a cohort group (RH only; LH only; matched; assessed but not used as selection criteria; not assessed)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has handedness

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the number of times a patient has been examined across time
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has longitudinal timepoint

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes inclusion criteria for maximum age of participants in a CohortGroup
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has max age

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes inclusion criteria for maximum IQ of participants in a CohortGroup
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has max IQ

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the mean age of the cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has mean age

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes inclusion criteria for minimum age of participants in a CohortGroup
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has min age

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes inclusion criteria for minimum IQ of participants in a CohortGroup
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has min IQ

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasNeurologicalComorbidity true --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who have two or more neurological disorders
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of a cohort group have a neurological comorbidity
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has neurological comorbidity

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of arterial spin labeling image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of ASL

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the number of cis female individuals in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of cis female

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the number of cis male individuals in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of cis male

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of electroencephalography image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of EEG

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the number of females in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of female

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the number of males in the cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of male

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: Cohort1 hasNumberOfParticipants 500 --> Cohort1 is made up of approximately 500 patients
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the number of participants in the cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of participants

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of susceptibility weighted imaging image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of SWI

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of T1-weighted image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of T1w

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of T2 image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of T2

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describing the number of female to male transgender individuals in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of transgender F to M

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describing the number of male to female transgender individuals in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of transgender m to f

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describing the number of individuals of undisclosed gender in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of undisclosed gender

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of diffusion MRI image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of dMRI

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of resting state fMRI image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of rsfMRI

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the amount of total body fat measured on MRI image data collected by a project cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has number of tbfMRI

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from blood/saliva collected/stored with NO DNA extracted
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent blood saliva collection

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from DNA extraction with no genotyping
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent DNA extraction no genotyping

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from blood epigenetics
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent epigenetics blood

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from saliva epigenetics
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent epigenetics saliva

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from exome sequencing
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent exome sequencing

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from gene expression
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent gene expression

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from genome-wide genotyping
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent genome-wide genotyping

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from mitochondrial genotyping
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent mitochondrial genotyping

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from plasma
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent plasma

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from select loci (some SNPs/CNVs)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent select loci

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from transcriptomics
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent transcriptomics

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the percent of cohort group biosamples which are from whole genome sequencing
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has percent whole genome sequencing

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the cohort has pregnant members
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has pregnant members

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 hasPsychiatricComorbidity true --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who have two or more pyschiatric disorders
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of a cohort group have a psychiatric comorbidity
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has psychiatric comorbidity

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether the genders of cohort group members were determined genetically
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has sex determined genetically

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the species of the subjects of a cohort (Humans, Chimps, Mice, etc.)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has species

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment:
Describes the study design of the cohort group or project (Case/control; Population; Healthy only; Patients only)
NOTE: study design options are mutually exclusive for Cohort Groups but not Projects
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has study design

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the study features of a cohort group (Clinical trial; Twin/Family study; Logitudinal; in-vivo; ex-vivo; post-mortem)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: has study feature

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether a cohort includes female participants
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: includes female

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether a cohort includes male participants
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: includes male

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example: CohortGroup1 isClinicallyStable yes --> CohortGroup1 only includes people who are clinically stable
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if the members of the cohort group are clinically stable (typically indicated by vital signs within 20% of usual readings)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: is clinically stable

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if a cohort study was family based
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: is family based

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes whether or not the members of the cohort group are proficient in local language
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: is proficient in local language

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes if a cohort's data is publicly available
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: is public

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the scanner used by the cohort
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: uses scanner

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasDisorderDetails Schizophrenia Schizophrenia withDisorderSeverity 5
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people with schizophrenia with disease severity 5
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the severity of the disease
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with disorder severity

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasDisorderDetails Schizophrenia Schizophrenia withMaxAgeOfOnsetOfDisorder 18
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people who had schizophrenia at 18 or younger
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the maximum age of onset of a disease
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with max age of onset of disorder

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasDisorderDetails Schizophrenia Schizophrenia withMaxDurationOfDisorder 20
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people who had bipolar disorder for at most 20 years
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the maximum duration (in years) of a disease
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with max duration of disorder

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasMedicalRatingDetails YoungManiaRatingScale YoungManiaRatingScale withMaxDurationOfDisorder 10
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people who received a score of at most 10 on the YMRS
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the maximum medical rating score of individuals included in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with max number

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasDisorderDetails Schizophrenia Schizophrenia withMinAgeOfOnsetOfDisorder 10
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people who had schizophrenia at 10 or older
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the minimum age of onset of a disease
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with min age of onset of disorder

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasDisorderDetails Schizophrenia Schizophrenia withMinDurationOfDisorder 10
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people had bipolar disorder for at least 10 years
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the minimum duration (in years) of a disease
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with min duration of disorder

owl:DatatypeProperty.vann:example:
CohortGroup1 hasMedicalRatingDetails YoungManiaRatingScale YoungManiaRatingScale withMaxDurationOfDisorder 0
--> CohortGroup1 only includes people who scored at least a 0 on the YMRS
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Describes the minimum medical rating score of individuals included in a cohort group
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: with min number

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A mental health disorder defined by feelings of anxiety, fear, or worry
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Anxiety Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Specifies the kinds of brain scan data collected
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Brain Scan Data Type

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Rating scale used to measure psychiatric symptoms among cohort members
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Brief Psychiatric Rating Scale

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A disease characterized by abnormal cell division and growth
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cancer

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A subset of vascular disorders affecting the heart
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cardiovascular Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A subset of vascular disorders affecting blood vessels of the brain and cerebral circulation
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cerebrovascular Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: City in which a cohort is located
owl:Class.rdfs:label: City

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Rating scale used to measure mental disorder symptom severity and treaments
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Clinical Global Impression Scale

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A group of individuals studied by a working group, limited by certain inclusion and exclusion criteria
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cohort

owl:Class.vann:example: AMCControlGroup is a control cohort group of the AMC cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A subset of Cohort, which either forms the patient group or control group
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cohort Group

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A state or mood experienced by the members of a cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Condition

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Country in which a cohort is located
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Country

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Specifies the kinds of data collected
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Data Type

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A dataset containing information about an ENIGMA project cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Dataset

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The method used to diagnosis individuals in a Cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Diagnosis Instrument

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The principles and standards used to diagnose a diease or condition
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Diagnostic Criteria

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A disorder/disease experienced by members of a cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Disorders which affect the endocrine system
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Endocrine Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Specifies the kinds of genetic data collected
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Genetic Data Type

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Disorders which are inherited and caused by abnormalities in the genome
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Genetic Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Software tools used for genotyping within a cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Genotype Platform

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Questionnaire used to measure the severity of depression
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Hamilton Depression Rating Scale

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Procedure used to collect image data within the cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Image Acquisition Protocol

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A disease or disorder caused by the invasion of microorganisms
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Infectious Disorder

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Method used to receive information about cohort subjects
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Information Obtainment Method

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Geographic location of the cohort
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Location

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Systems or scales used to measure the severity of a medical condition
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Medical Rating

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Disorders which can affect mood, behavior, and thinking
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Mental Health Disorder
